title: Penny Arcade - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"PENNY ARCADE" Web Comic

"Penny Arcade," written by Jerry Holkins and illustrated by Mike Krahulik, is a Web comic focused on video games and video game culture.  The comic debuted in November of 1998, and is among the most popular and longest running gaming comics currently online.

This torrent collects "Penny Arcade" comics from the strip's debut through the end of 2014.  The comics are compiled into a set of CBR files, one for each year.  (1998 and 1999 are combined into a single file.)  Each comic's page includes its date and title
